<P>
Photo, Loyola's Tina Hammers,left, and Stacy Trapp go for block against UCLA. 
They play tonight. ALAN HAGMAN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Kerry House is one 
of the spark plugs of a struggling Loyola team. 
</P>
