</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Karen Strickholm has been promoted to vice president in the corporate 
entertainment division of the public relations firm Rogers &amp; Cowan, Los 
Angeles. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA090889-0072 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 104693 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 8, 1989, Friday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part 6; Page 1; Column 5; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
