POLITICAL ACTIVISM; AUTOMOBILE INSURANCE; PROPOSITION 103 (STATE INSURANCE 
COMMISSIONER); LEGISLATION -- CALIFORNIA; GILLESPIE, ROXANI M; COLLIS, CONWAY 
