RELATIONS -- SOUTH AFRICA; SOUTH AFRICA -- ELECTIONS; GOVERNMENT REFORM; 
AFRICAN NATIONAL CONGRESS; DE KLERK, FREDERIK W; THATCHER, MARGARET; ECONOMIC 
